  "title": "🎲Game Dealers | $2400 - $2900",
  "description": "<h1>🎲<strong>Game Dealers | Up to $2900 + Benefits | Central </strong></h1><p>Step into the world of excitement and high energy! <em><strong>No experience? No problem — full training will be provided.</strong></em><br /></p><p>📍 <strong>Location</strong>: Singapore<br />💵 <strong>Salary</strong>: Up to $2900/month + AWS + Performance Bonus + Incentives<br />🕒 <strong>Shifts</strong>: Rotating Morning / Noon / Night (night transport provided)<br />🍽 <strong>Meals</strong>: Provided during shifts</p><h3>🃏 <strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Deal table games professionally while delivering top-notch customer service.</li><li>Monitor game integrity and promptly report any suspicious activity.</li><li>Follow standard dealing procedures and stay updated on changes.</li><li>Respond to alerts from the Operations Control Room.</li></ul><h3>✅ <strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li>No minimum education required.</li><li>Willing to commit to rotating shift work (including weekends/public holidays).</li><li>No prior experience needed — <strong>comprehensive training provided</strong>.</li><li>Professional, attentive, and enjoys working in a fast-paced environment.</li></ul><h3>✨ <strong>Why Join Us?</strong></h3><ul><li>Competitive salary with bonuses and incentives.</li><li>Full training programme to kick-start your career as a Game Dealer.</li><li>Night transport and meals provided.</li><li>Dynamic, supportive team environment.</li></ul><p>📩 <strong>Apply Now!</strong></p><p>Send your resume in MS Word format to: <strong>Vanessa.chua@crew.sg</strong></p><p>Please include your <strong>availability, notice period, and expected salary.</strong></p><p><em>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Vanessa Chua Peng Teng (R25158315)</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by Hrnet</p><p>E.A. 24C2435<br />\n\n</p>",
